{"tid":498352,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"[倉鼠JJ入]有無巴絲知道身後硬塊係咩？","createTime":"2017-12-13T16:41:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-13T17:48:21.000Z","uid":63765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6a97af86d87afe5d5095e1075b8d28d07abfa848","tid":498352,"uid":63765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T16:41:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/14/003110_801c8da137626e980a5917edf2d1f257.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F14%2F003110_801c8da137626e980a5917edf2d1f257.jpg&h=749178da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如圖 <br />\n本身我有養開兩隻倉鼠 <br />\n有一次我本身拎起呢倉鼠嗰時<br />\n先發現佢背側有塊突起咗一塊嘅硬塊 唔知你哋睇得清唔清楚 就係左邊背側會見到有嗰位有啲唔同<br />\n有無巴絲打知道係咩嚟？我上網搵過但都好似搵唔到咁 又唔似係腫瘤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我同呢隻倉鼠感情好好 真係唔想佢有時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad61211845724dbb1bd805ce9dc0102f0a315424","tid":498352,"uid":63765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T16:46:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/14/004638_daff67d995958a694d35727c676d8044.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F14%2F004638_daff67d995958a694d35727c676d8044.jpg&h=9925a50a&s={SIZE}\" />影多張清楚啲嘅"},{"pid":"05ac428c7e04b523928ca69f60fcd797b4dee8ff","tid":498352,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T17:48:21.000Z","msg":"可能係腫瘤<br />\n倉鼠好易有<br />\n(鳩up)"}]}